Ikachan (HTTP-to-IRC Gateway)
=============================

Ikachan is an httpd to deliver messages to IRC.
http://search.cpan.org/~yappo/App-Ikachan/bin/ikachan

This service lets you publish event messages to IRC through Ikachan httpd.

Install Notes
-------------

1. *url*(REQUIRED) - Ikachan server base url, ex. http://example.jp:4979/
2. *room*(REQUIRED) - Supports single or multiple rooms (comma separated).
